project_descr: Clearing unexploded ordnance (UXO) contaminated land remains a particular challenge for Lao PDR. When SDGs were adopted, it was therefore agreed to introduce a national SDG 18 on Removing the UXO Obstacle to Human Development.

outputs.output_descr: At the end of the initiation plan it is expected that awareness, coordination and collaboration on the SDGs is enhanced, strengthening the enabling environment for the achievement of SDG-18 in particular.

project_title: promote enabling envrm for sdg achievement, incld sdg18
